</REFSECT1INFO>
<TITLE>Description
</TITLE>
<PARA>
<FUNCTION>sem_timedwait</FUNCTION> waits for semaphore object 
<SYMBOL>SEM</SYMBOL> being posted. It is a new function from 
<CITETITLE PUBWORK="BOOK">IEEE Std. 1003.1-200x</CITETITLE> that 
is similar to <FUNCTION>sem_wait</FUNCTION> but waits only until 
<SYMBOL>ABSTIME</SYMBOL>.
</PARA>
</REFSECT1>
